Gap when playing videos end to end  :(

--layer option lets mutliple videos play with one being visible...  can use this for blank loop...

Loop option fails.

Building more recent omxplayer:

git clone https://github.com/popcornmix/omxplayer.git
cd omxplayer
./prepare-native-raspbian.sh
sudo apt-get install ca-certificates git-core subversion binutils libva1 libpcre3-dev libidn11-dev libboost1.50-dev libfreetype6-dev libusb-1.0-0-dev libdbus-1-dev libssl-dev libssh-dev libsmbclient-dev gcc-4.7 g++-4.7 sed pkg-config

